        <releasenotes>
            <![CDATA[
            <h3>Version 2.0.33 - PostMessage Reload for SmartLearning Integration</h3>

            <h4>Improvement</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Send scorm-reload-embed postMessage to parent instead of window.reload</li>
                <li>SmartLearning Vue app can handle reload more elegantly</li>
                <li>Prevents cascading re-initialization of the Vue app</li>
                <li>Fallback to window.location.reload() if postMessage fails</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Technical Details</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Message type: 'scorm-reload-embed' with cmid, slide, timestamp</li>
                <li>Posts to all parent frames up to window.top</li>
                <li>If messageSent, wait for parent to handle reload</li>
                <li>More elegant than full page reload for embedded contexts</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Previous Versions</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>v2.0.32: Anti-reload-loop with separate tracking key</li>
                <li>v2.0.31: Add skipReload param to navigateToSlide</li>
                <li>v2.0.30: Re-enable direct navigation fallback</li>
                <li>v2.0.29: Comprehensive suspend_data field modification</li>
            </ul>
            ]]>
        </releasenotes>
